                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_7086984801760748.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ah",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Rhinedottir lived in Khaenri'ah during the Eclipse Dynasty. She was one of the six people who should have prevented the disaster and stopped the Vinster King from continuing to rock the foundation of the world. She, along with four of them, couldn't resist the call of the Abyss and divided among themselves a power that could destroy the world. She became a Sinner, a transcendent being with a world-shattering power. Her creations invaded Teyvat during the Cataclysm 500 years ago.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
